{ INITIALIZATION EQUATIONS }
: s ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation = 30
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Aggregate indicator of environmental health. Higher values mean more degradation.
: s ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality = 70
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Handicraft_Activities = 15
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement = 10
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."Indigenous_Community_Well-Being" = 30
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Knowledge = 80
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Represents the vitality and transmission of traditional indigenous knowledge
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_Engagement = 30
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Deforestation_Awareness = 20
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness = 10
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity = 20
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.People_Trust_in_Institutions = 20
    UNITS: Percentage
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Cleared_Land_Area = 7
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area = 40
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Total forest area including Indigenous Forest Area.
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area = 25
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Percentage of the total area that is Forest and also legally recognized as Indigenous Land. This area benefits from special protection but is still subject to pressures.
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Legal_Timber_Extraction_Area = 5
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Pasture_Area = 48
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.forest_area_impact_on_soil_recovery = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area / (INIT (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area * 2))
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: 100
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_RAW_MATERIAL_AVAILABILITY = 0,02
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".availability_of_raw_material_for_handicraft = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area/INIT (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area)) * (1 - ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) * BASE_RAW_MATERIAL_AVAILABILITY+ 3*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right
    DOCUMENT: More indigenous forest area, more material
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE = 0,001
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_conservation_policy = 0
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Forest_conservation_policy ELSE 0
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_recovery_rate =  BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE + FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_HUMAN_FIRE_RATE = 0,008
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS = TIME
    UNITS: Days
    DOCUMENT: Values from D3.8 using SSP2-4.5 
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.climate_dryness_effect = IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 10 THEN 1  ELSE IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 30 THEN 1,5  ELSE IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 50 THEN 1,8  ELSE 2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_engagement_initiatives = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Women_engagement_initiatives ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Education_and_knowledge_transfer = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES = IF TIME > 2035 THEN Education_and_knowledge_transfer ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Community_engagement = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION = IF TIME > 2035 THEN Community_engagement ELSE 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness = "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS + 2*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES+4*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.human_induced_fire_rate =  BASE_HUMAN_FIRE_RATE * climate_dryness_effect * (1 - 0,2 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.fire_induced_deforestation_rate = (human_induced_fire_rate)*(Forest_Area/100)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_PASTURE_EXPANSION_RATE = 0,3
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This is the ‘potential’ expansion rate of pastures, under standard conditions (profitability=1 and available land). 0.5%land/year means a slow growth; 1//year means a moderate growth, while 2%/year means an aggressive growth.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR = 2 * (1 - 0,1 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Economic return from grazing expansion on a scale of 0 to 2 (1=basic situation)
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.MAX_PASTURE_AREA_LIMIT = 70
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: maximum proportion of land that can realistically be converted to pasture.
    It serves to artificially curb expansion when pastures approach this limit. 70% realistic average limit; 80% extreme limit (quite total saturation); 60% conservative scenario (strong protection/restoration).
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_expansion_demand_rate =   BASE_PASTURE_EXPANSION_RATE * PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR   * (1 - Pasture_Area/MAX_PASTURE_AREA_LIMIT)   * (1 - 0,3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_NON_INDIGENOUS = 0,004
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous = ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_NON_INDIGENOUS*(Forest_Area-Indigenous_Forest_Area)*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This represents the annual rate at which forest area is lost due to illegal logging activities, contributing to overall deforestation.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.LAND_GRABBING_BASE_RATE = 0,003
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.CLEARING_EFFECTIVENESS_FACTOR = 0,8
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: A value of 0.8 suggests that 80% of land grabbing results in direct pressure for deforestation. reflects the effectiveness (or legality/illegality) of land grabbing, where not all of the land grabbed is immediately or effectively deforested, due to obstacles or inefficient management.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest = LAND_GRABBING_BASE_RATE * CLEARING_EFFECTIVENESS_FACTOR * (Forest_Area - Indigenous_Forest_Area) / Forest_Area
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Pressure from land grabbing on non-indigenous parts of the forest
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.TOTAL_TIMBER_DEMAND = 2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.TIMBER_CLEARING_FACTOR = 0,1 * (1 - 0,1 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_clearing_demand_rate = TOTAL_TIMBER_DEMAND*TIMBER_CLEARING_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This rate reflects how much new forest area needs to be cleared each year to meet the legal timber demand. It's the part of the total demand that leads to direct deforestation for legal timber production, converting forest into cleared land. Assumed to be on non-Indigenous forest only.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE = 0,002
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.ILLEGAL_PASTURE_ENFORCEMENT_FACTOR = 1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous = BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE*(1+(PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR-1))*ILLEGAL_PASTURE_ENFORCEMENT_FACTOR* (Forest_Area - Indigenous_Forest_Area) / Forest_Area*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.deforestation_from_clearing = pasture_expansion_demand_rate+illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+legal_timber_clearing_demand_rate+illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE_INDIGENOUS = 0,002
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.MAX_INDIGENOUS_FOREST_AREA = 30
    UNITS: Percentage
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_recovery_rate_in_indigenous_land = BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE_INDIGENOUS * (1 - Indigenous_Forest_Area/MAX_INDIGENOUS_FOREST_AREA) + FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES+Secure_indigenous_land_right
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land = (LAND_GRABBING_BASE_RATE * CLEARING_EFFECTIVENESS_FACTOR)* (Indigenous_Forest_Area / Forest_Area)*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_INDIGENOUS = 0,002
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
    DOCUMENT: Lower that non indigenous due to protection from natives
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.lack_of_property_right_factor = (1/(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY *"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT))
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.property_rights_effectiveness = 1/(1+lack_of_property_right_factor)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_FOREST_POLICY = 0,5
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Increase_market_accessibility = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS = IF TIME > 2035 THEN "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Training_and_capacity_building = 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Training_and_capacity_building ELSE 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation = 0
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_protection_policy_effectiveness = BASE_FOREST_POLICY + (INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT ) + 0,09*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR   + 0,09*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS+0,9*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT+0,9*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION+0,9*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land = ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_INDIGENOUS * Indigenous_Forest_Area* (1-(property_rights_effectiveness+forest_protection_policy_effectiveness))*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE_INDIGENOUS = 0,0008
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Lower than illegal pasture rate (non-indigenous) due to protection from natives
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land = (BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE_INDIGENOUS * (1+(PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR-1)) * ILLEGAL_PASTURE_ENFORCEMENT_FACTOR * (Indigenous_Forest_Area / Forest_Area))*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.deforestation_in_indigenous_land = (land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land+illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land+illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of deforestation occurring specifically within Indigenous Forest Areas
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate =  (fire_induced_deforestation_rate + deforestation_from_clearing + deforestation_in_indigenous_land) * (1 -( forest_protection_policy_effectiveness))
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.PASTURE_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR = 0,0005
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_abandonment_rate = Pasture_Area*PASTURE_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.TIMBER_EXPANSION_FACTOR = 0,05
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_expansion_rate = TOTAL_TIMBER_DEMAND*TIMBER_EXPANSION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This rate indicates how quickly the dedicated 'Legal Timber Extraction Areas' are expanding each year. It's driven by the overall timber demand and represents the growth of land specifically managed for legal timber harvesting.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.TIMBER_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY = 0,6
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.conversion_to_legal_timber_extraction = legal_timber_expansion_rate*TIMBER_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY*(Cleared_Land_Area/100)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.LEGAL_TIMBER_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR = 0,02
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_extraction_abandonment_rate = Legal_Timber_Extraction_Area*LEGAL_TIMBER_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.newly_cleared_land = total_deforestation_rate+pasture_abandonment_rate+legal_timber_extraction_abandonment_rate
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: All deforested land first becomes 'Cleared_land' before conversion
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.PASTURE_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY = 0,9
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.conversion_to_pasture_area = pasture_expansion_demand_rate*PASTURE_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY*(DELAY((Cleared_Land_Area); 2))
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Cleared land area available for pasture conversion after a delay period.
: c Coordination_costs = 5
: c Education_cost = 5
: c Engagement_cost = 5
: c Forest_restoration_cost = 5
: c land_right_cost = 5
: c Market_access_cost = 5
: c Monitoring_cost = 5
: c Women_Engagement_cost = 5
: c Training_costs = 5
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Engagement = 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Enhance_environmental_monitoring = 0
: c Overall_strategy_cost = ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Increase_market_accessibility*Market_access_cost)+(land_right_cost*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_engagement_initiatives*Women_Engagement_cost)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Education_and_knowledge_transfer*Education_cost)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Training_and_capacity_building*Training_costs)+(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation*Coordination_costs)+(Engagement_cost*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Engagement)+(Forest_restoration_cost*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_conservation_policy)+(Monitoring_cost*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Enhance_environmental_monitoring)
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.DEFORESTATION_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,6
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.deforestation_impact_on_environmental_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate * DEFORESTATION_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.PASTURE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,6
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.pasture_expansion_impact_on_environmental_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_expansion_demand_rate*PASTURE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.FIRE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,6
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.fire_impact_on_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.fire_induced_deforestation_rate*FIRE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.ILLEGAL_ACTIVITIES_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,6
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.illegal_activities_impact_on_environmental_degradation = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land) * ILLEGAL_ACTIVITIES_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Combined impact of all illegal activities (both indigenous and non-indigenous areas) on environmental degradation. The impact of illegal activities on the environment is not only a function of the area converted/deforested, but also of the way in which the activity is conducted, and this method is inherently more destructive when the activity is illegal and unregulated.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_SOIL_QUALITY = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.SOIL_DEGRADATION_AMPLIFIER = 0,2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Amplifies environmental degradation rate when soil quality is low
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.conservation_impact_on_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES+INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.degradation_rate = (deforestation_impact_on_environmental_degradation + pasture_expansion_impact_on_environmental_degradation + fire_impact_on_degradation + illegal_activities_impact_on_environmental_degradation) * (1 - Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION)* (1 + (1 - Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) * SOIL_DEGRADATION_AMPLIFIER)-conservation_impact_on_degradation
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Total rate of environmental degradation, influenced by various human activities. The (1 - ...) term ensures it slows down as degradation approaches its maximum.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.BASE_ENVIRONMENTAL_RECOVERY_RATE = 0,005
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: 0,005
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Base_policy_effectiveness = 1
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.environmental_policy_effectiveness = Base_policy_effectiveness*(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity+INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Overall effectiveness of environmental policies (0=none, 1=perfect). Higher values enhance recovery.
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.environmental_recovery_rate = BASE_ENVIRONMENTAL_RECOVERY_RATE * (1 + environmental_policy_effectiveness) * (Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of environmental recovery, enhanced by policy effectiveness and faster when degradation is high.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.BASE_SOIL_RECOVERY_RATE = 0,003
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION_IMPACT_ON_SOIL_RECOVERY = 0,5
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Factor by which high environmental degradation hinders soil recovery.
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.soil_recovery_rate = BASE_SOIL_RECOVERY_RATE * (1 - Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) * (1 + forest_area_impact_on_soil_recovery)* (1 - (Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) * ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION_IMPACT_ON_SOIL_RECOVERY)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of soil quality recovery. It slows down as soil quality approaches its maximum, and is enhanced by larger forest areas.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.PASTURE_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,008
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.pasture_impact_on_soil_quality = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Pasture_Area*PASTURE_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.DEFORESTATION_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,01
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.deforestation_impact_on_soil_quality = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate*DEFORESTATION_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.ILLEGAL_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR = 0,005
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.illegal_activities_impact_on_soil_quality = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land)*ILLEGAL_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.soil_degradation_rate = (pasture_impact_on_soil_quality + deforestation_impact_on_soil_quality+illegal_activities_impact_on_soil_quality) * (Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of soil quality degradation due to human activities. It slows down as soil quality approaches zero.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."WELL-BEING_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR" = 0,00001
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."indigenous_community_well-being_impact_on_engagement" = "Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"*"WELL-BEING_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR"
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Higher well-being fosters greater community engagement
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".institutional_capacity_for_engagement = INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".policy_engagement_initiatives_impact = institutional_capacity_for_engagement+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Engagement_initiatives = Engagement*100
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".increasing_engagement = ("indigenous_community_well-being_impact_on_engagement" + policy_engagement_initiatives_impact+Engagement_initiatives) * (1 - Indigenous_Community_Engagement / MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_PEOPLE_TRUST = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".PEOPLE_TRUST_DECLINE_FACTOR = 1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".people_trust_in_institutions_decline = (1 - INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.People_Trust_in_Institutions / INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_PEOPLE_TRUST) * PEOPLE_TRUST_DECLINE_FACTOR
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".TRUST_DECLINE_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR = 0,08
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".trust_decline_impact_on_egagement = people_trust_in_institutions_decline*TRUST_DECLINE_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".CULTURAL_EROSION_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR = 1,2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".CULTURAL_EROSION_BASE_RATE = 4
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."MAX_WELL-BEING" = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_contribution =  CULTURAL_EROSION_BASE_RATE   * MAX(0; (1 - "Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"/"MAX_WELL-BEING"))   * (1 - 0,2 * EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES      )
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_impact_on_indigenous_engagement = CULTURAL_EROSION_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR*cultural_erosion_contribution
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".decreasing_engagement = ((trust_decline_impact_on_egagement+cultural_erosion_impact_on_indigenous_engagement)*Indigenous_Community_Engagement/MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_ACCESS_TO_MARKET = 0,35
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".access_to_market = BASE_ACCESS_TO_MARKET
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_FINANCIAL_SUPPORT = 0,12
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".financial_support_handicraft = BASE_FINANCIAL_SUPPORT
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COMMUNITY_SUPPORT_FACTOR = 0,01
    UNITS: 1/Percentage
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".community_support_handicraft = (Indigenous_Community_Engagement+2*Women_Engagement+2*Indigenous_Knowledge)*COMMUNITY_SUPPORT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_HANDICRAFT_ACTIVITIES = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".empowerment_impact_on_creation = FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_creation = (availability_of_raw_material_for_handicraft * access_to_market * financial_support_handicraft * community_support_handicraft) * (1 - Handicraft_Activities / MAX_HANDICRAFT_ACTIVITIES) * (1 + MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR) + empowerment_impact_on_creation + AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS+EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES+(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation/2)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COMPETITION_PRESSURE_HANDICRAFT = 0,015
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_IMPACT_ON_COMPETITION = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_closure = Handicraft_Activities * COMPETITION_PRESSURE_HANDICRAFT * (1 - MARKET_ACCESS_IMPACT_ON_COMPETITION)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_activities_contribution_to_knowledge = Handicraft_Activities * (Handicraft_Activities / MAX_HANDICRAFT_ACTIVITIES)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".ENGAGEMENT_KNOWLEDGE_FACTOR = 0,00001
    UNITS: 1/Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".engagement_contribution_to_knowledge = (Indigenous_Community_Engagement+Women_Engagement)*ENGAGEMENT_KNOWLEDGE_FACTOR+4*COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".knowledge_gain_rate =   (4*handicraft_activities_contribution_to_knowledge + engagement_contribution_to_knowledge) * (1 - Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".knowledge_loss_rate = ((cultural_erosion_contribution)*Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."HANDICRAFT_WELL-BEING_FACTOR" = 0,00001
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."handicraft_contribution_to_well-being" = (Handicraft_Activities * "HANDICRAFT_WELL-BEING_FACTOR")
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."ENVIRONMENTAL_WELL-BEING_FACTOR" = 0,00001
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."environmental_quality_contribution_to_well-being" = (1-ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION)*"ENVIRONMENTAL_WELL-BEING_FACTOR"*(ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_SOIL_QUALITY)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Contribution of environmental quality (low degradation, high soil quality) to indigenous well-being.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."KNOWLEDGE_WELL-BEING_FACTOR" = 0,00001
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."indigenous_knowledge_contribution_to_well-being" = Indigenous_Knowledge*"KNOWLEDGE_WELL-BEING_FACTOR"
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."well-being_increase" = ("handicraft_contribution_to_well-being"+"environmental_quality_contribution_to_well-being"+"indigenous_knowledge_contribution_to_well-being"+0,9*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation)*(1-"Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"/"MAX_WELL-BEING")
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Factors contributing to the increase in indigenous well-being. Slows down as max well-being is approached.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".RESOURCE_SCARCITY_IMPACT_FACTOR = 0,02
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".resources_scarcity_impact = ( (ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation / ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) + (1 - ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality / ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) ) / 2 * RESOURCE_SCARCITY_IMPACT_FACTOR
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_AMPLIFIER = 0,2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_RATE = 0,1
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".social_disruption_impact = ( (cultural_erosion_contribution / CULTURAL_EROSION_BASE_RATE) * SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_AMPLIFIER * BASE_SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_RATE)/(Women_Engagement/100)
    UNITS: 1/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."well-being_decrease" = (resources_scarcity_impact+social_disruption_impact)*"Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_WOMEN_ACCESS_TO_RESOURCES = 0,001
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".HANDICRAFT_IMPACT_ON_WOMEN_RESOURCES = 0,001
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Percentage
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_access_to_resources = BASE_WOMEN_ACCESS_TO_RESOURCES * (1 + Handicraft_Activities * HANDICRAFT_IMPACT_ON_WOMEN_RESOURCES) + FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_WOMEN_INITATIVES = 0,001
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".institutional_capacity_for_women_initiatives = INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_initiatives_impact = (BASE_WOMEN_INITATIVES*institutional_capacity_for_women_initiatives)+Women_engagement_initiatives
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_WOMEN_ENGAGEMENT = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_increase_rate = (women_access_to_resources+women_engagement_initiatives_impact)*(1-Women_Engagement/MAX_WOMEN_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_CULTURAL_BARRIERS = 0,05
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_barriers_to_engagement = BASE_CULTURAL_BARRIERS*(1-Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Traditional knowledge may reduce barriers
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".CULTURAL_EROSION_WOMEN_FACTOR = 1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_impact_on_women_engagement = cultural_erosion_contribution*CULTURAL_EROSION_WOMEN_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_reduction_rate = ((cultural_barriers_to_engagement+cultural_erosion_impact_on_women_engagement)*Women_Engagement/MAX_WOMEN_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".BASE_ENGAGEMENT_INITIATIVES = 0,00001
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".HANDICRAFT_KNOWLEDGE_FACTOR = 0,00001
    UNITS: 1/Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Social_disruption_barrier = social_disruption_impact*100
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.EDUCATION_CAMPAIGNS_EFFECTIVENESS = 0,1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.BASE_INFORMATION_SHARING = 10
    UNITS: Percentage
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.information_sharing_effectiveness = IF Institutional_Capacity < 40 THEN 10 ELSE IF Institutional_Capacity < 80 THEN 70 ELSE 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.information_sharing_with_the_community = BASE_INFORMATION_SHARING   + (Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness * information_sharing_effectiveness)   + ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement * 0,03)   + 2 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES   + 3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS
    UNITS: Percentage
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_DEFORESTATION_AWARENESS = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.increasing_awareness =   EDUCATION_CAMPAIGNS_EFFECTIVENESS * information_sharing_with_the_community   * (1 - Deforestation_Awareness / MAX_DEFORESTATION_AWARENESS)   + 0,2 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES   + 0,3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.AWARENESS_DECAY_RATE = 0,1
    UNITS: 1/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.decreasing_awareness = Deforestation_Awareness*AWARENESS_DECAY_RATE
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRAINING_INVESTMENTS = Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Level of investments in institutional personal training
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.training_investments_effective = TRAINING_INVESTMENTS+1*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRAINING_INVESTMENT_EFFECTIVENESS = 0,05
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Effectiveness of investments in training.
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.BASE_INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION = 0,1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION = BASE_INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION+1*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION+Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.INVESTMENTS_IN_INSTITUTIONAL_COOPERATION = Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_CAPACITY_FACTOR = 0,01
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.people_trust_in_institutions_impact_on_capacity = People_Trust_in_Institutions*TRUST_CAPACITY_FACTOR+TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.increasing_capacity =   ( training_investments_effective * TRAINING_INVESTMENT_EFFECTIVENESS * (0,5 + 0,3*MIN(1; "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT                   + "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION))   + INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION * INVESTMENTS_IN_INSTITUTIONAL_COOPERATION * (0,5 + 0,3*MIN(1; "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT                   + "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION))   + people_trust_in_institutions_impact_on_capacity * (0,5 + 0,2*public_awareness) )   * (1 - Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY)   + 0,2 * LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES   + 0,3 * LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.INSTITUTIONAL_INSTABILITY = 0,3
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.CORRUPTION_LEVEL = 0,8
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.decreasing_capacity = (INSTITUTIONAL_INSTABILITY * CORRUPTION_LEVEL*2) * Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.ENVIRONMENTAL_MONITORING_FUNDING = Enhance_environmental_monitoring
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.REQUIRED_MONITORING_FUNDING = 1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.institutional_capacity_impact_on_monitoring = Institutional_Capacity/MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.EFFECTIVENESS_BUILD_RATE = Enhance_environmental_monitoring
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_MONITORING_EFFECTIVENESS = 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.monitoring_increase = (ENVIRONMENTAL_MONITORING_FUNDING/ REQUIRED_MONITORING_FUNDING) * institutional_capacity_impact_on_monitoring * EFFECTIVENESS_BUILD_RATE * 50*(1 - Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness / MAX_MONITORING_EFFECTIVENESS)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.BASE_DECAY_RATE_MONITORING = 0,05
    UNITS: 1/Year
    DOCUMENT: Base rate of deterioration in monitoring effectiveness.
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.monitoring_decrease = Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness * BASE_DECAY_RATE_MONITORING *(1+ (1 - Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY)*0,5)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_GAIN_PER_PARTICIPATION = 0,2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Gain in trust per unit of participation in the indigenous community.
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_GAIN_FOR_WELL_BEING = 0,5
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Gain in trust per unit of well-being of the indigenous community.
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_GAINED_PER_INFORMATION_UNIT = 0,1
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Gain in trust per unit of information shared with the community.
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_BONUS_AWARE = 0,05
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.trust_increase =  MIN(   ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement * TRUST_GAIN_PER_PARTICIPATION * 0,01) + ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."Indigenous_Community_Well-Being" * TRUST_GAIN_FOR_WELL_BEING * 0,01)+  ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_Engagement * TRUST_GAIN_PER_PARTICIPATION * 0,01) + (information_sharing_with_the_community * TRUST_GAINED_PER_INFORMATION_UNIT * 0,01) + TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS + TRUST_BONUS_AWARE * public_awareness ; (MAX_PEOPLE_TRUST - People_Trust_in_Institutions))
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRUST_REDUCTION_PER_CORRUPTION = 0,5
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.trust_decrease = MIN(  CORRUPTION_LEVEL * (1 - 0,25*public_awareness) * TRUST_REDUCTION_PER_CORRUPTION * 5 * People_Trust_in_Institutions / MAX_PEOPLE_TRUST ;   People_Trust_in_Institutions )
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Awareness_barrier = 100-Deforestation_Awareness
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Monitoring_barrier = 100-Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Trust_barrier = 100-People_Trust_in_Institutions
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Policy_enforcement_barrier = 100-(forest_protection_policy_effectiveness*100)

{ RUNTIME EQUATIONS }
: s ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation(t) = Environmental_Degradation(t - dt) + (degradation_rate - environmental_recovery_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Aggregate indicator of environmental health. Higher values mean more degradation.
: s ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality(t) = Soil_Quality(t - dt) + (soil_recovery_rate - soil_degradation_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Handicraft_Activities(t) = Handicraft_Activities(t - dt) + (handicraft_creation - handicraft_closure) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement(t) = Indigenous_Community_Engagement(t - dt) + (increasing_engagement - decreasing_engagement) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"(t) = "Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"(t - dt) + ("well-being_increase" - "well-being_decrease") * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Knowledge(t) = Indigenous_Knowledge(t - dt) + (knowledge_gain_rate - knowledge_loss_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Represents the vitality and transmission of traditional indigenous knowledge
: s "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_Engagement(t) = Women_Engagement(t - dt) + (women_engagement_increase_rate - women_engagement_reduction_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Deforestation_Awareness(t) = Deforestation_Awareness(t - dt) + (increasing_awareness - decreasing_awareness) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness(t) = Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness(t - dt) + (monitoring_increase - monitoring_decrease) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity(t) = Institutional_Capacity(t - dt) + (increasing_capacity - decreasing_capacity) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.People_Trust_in_Institutions(t) = People_Trust_in_Institutions(t - dt) + (trust_increase - trust_decrease) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Cleared_Land_Area(t) = Cleared_Land_Area(t - dt) + (newly_cleared_land - conversion_to_pasture_area - conversion_to_legal_timber_extraction) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area(t) = Forest_Area(t - dt) + (forest_recovery_rate - total_deforestation_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Total forest area including Indigenous Forest Area.
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area(t) = Indigenous_Forest_Area(t - dt) + (forest_recovery_rate_in_indigenous_land - deforestation_in_indigenous_land) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Percentage of the total area that is Forest and also legally recognized as Indigenous Land. This area benefits from special protection but is still subject to pressures.
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Legal_Timber_Extraction_Area(t) = Legal_Timber_Extraction_Area(t - dt) + (conversion_to_legal_timber_extraction - legal_timber_extraction_abandonment_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: s LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Pasture_Area(t) = Pasture_Area(t - dt) + (conversion_to_pasture_area - pasture_abandonment_rate) * dt {NON-NEGATIVE}
    UNITS: Percentage
    DOCUMENT: Mapbiomas data for Rondônia
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.forest_area_impact_on_soil_recovery = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area / (INIT (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_Area * 2))
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".availability_of_raw_material_for_handicraft = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area/INIT (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Indigenous_Forest_Area)) * (1 - ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) * BASE_RAW_MATERIAL_AVAILABILITY+ 3*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right
    DOCUMENT: More indigenous forest area, more material
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Forest_conservation_policy ELSE 0
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_recovery_rate =  BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE + FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS = GRAPH(TIME)
Points: (1,00, 55,0), (5,00, 42,0), (10,00, 62,0), (15,00, 55,3), (20,00, 50,0), (25,00, 61,0), (30,00, 53,0), (35,00, 55,1), (40,00, 52,9), (45,00, 55,0), (50,00, 40,0)
    UNITS: Days
    DOCUMENT: Values from D3.8 using SSP2-4.5 
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.climate_dryness_effect = IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 10 THEN 1  ELSE IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 30 THEN 1,5  ELSE IF CONSECUTIVE_DRY_DAYS < 50 THEN 1,8  ELSE 2
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Women_engagement_initiatives ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES = IF TIME > 2035 THEN Education_and_knowledge_transfer ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION = IF TIME > 2035 THEN Community_engagement ELSE 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness = "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS + 2*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES+4*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.human_induced_fire_rate =  BASE_HUMAN_FIRE_RATE * climate_dryness_effect * (1 - 0,2 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.fire_induced_deforestation_rate = (human_induced_fire_rate)*(Forest_Area/100)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR = 2 * (1 - 0,1 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Economic return from grazing expansion on a scale of 0 to 2 (1=basic situation)
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_expansion_demand_rate =   BASE_PASTURE_EXPANSION_RATE * PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR   * (1 - Pasture_Area/MAX_PASTURE_AREA_LIMIT)   * (1 - 0,3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous = ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_NON_INDIGENOUS*(Forest_Area-Indigenous_Forest_Area)*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This represents the annual rate at which forest area is lost due to illegal logging activities, contributing to overall deforestation.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest = LAND_GRABBING_BASE_RATE * CLEARING_EFFECTIVENESS_FACTOR * (Forest_Area - Indigenous_Forest_Area) / Forest_Area
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Pressure from land grabbing on non-indigenous parts of the forest
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.TIMBER_CLEARING_FACTOR = 0,1 * (1 - 0,1 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_clearing_demand_rate = TOTAL_TIMBER_DEMAND*TIMBER_CLEARING_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This rate reflects how much new forest area needs to be cleared each year to meet the legal timber demand. It's the part of the total demand that leads to direct deforestation for legal timber production, converting forest into cleared land. Assumed to be on non-Indigenous forest only.
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous = BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE*(1+(PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR-1))*ILLEGAL_PASTURE_ENFORCEMENT_FACTOR* (Forest_Area - Indigenous_Forest_Area) / Forest_Area*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.deforestation_from_clearing = pasture_expansion_demand_rate+illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+legal_timber_clearing_demand_rate+illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_recovery_rate_in_indigenous_land = BASE_FOREST_RECOVERY_RATE_INDIGENOUS * (1 - Indigenous_Forest_Area/MAX_INDIGENOUS_FOREST_AREA) + FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES+Secure_indigenous_land_right {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land = (LAND_GRABBING_BASE_RATE * CLEARING_EFFECTIVENESS_FACTOR)* (Indigenous_Forest_Area / Forest_Area)*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.lack_of_property_right_factor = (1/(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY *"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT))
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.property_rights_effectiveness = 1/(1+lack_of_property_right_factor)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS = IF TIME > 2035 THEN "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Training_and_capacity_building ELSE 0
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.forest_protection_policy_effectiveness = BASE_FOREST_POLICY + (INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement/"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT ) + 0,09*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR   + 0,09*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS+0,9*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT+0,9*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION+0,9*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land = ILLEGAL_LOGGING_PRESSURE_INDIGENOUS * Indigenous_Forest_Area* (1-(property_rights_effectiveness+forest_protection_policy_effectiveness))*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land = (BASE_ILLEGAL_PASTURE_RATE_INDIGENOUS * (1+(PASTURE_PROFITABILITY_FACTOR-1)) * ILLEGAL_PASTURE_ENFORCEMENT_FACTOR * (Indigenous_Forest_Area / Forest_Area))*1 - MIN(0,3; 0,5 * INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.public_awareness)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.deforestation_in_indigenous_land = (land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land+illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land+illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of deforestation occurring specifically within Indigenous Forest Areas
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate =  (fire_induced_deforestation_rate + deforestation_from_clearing + deforestation_in_indigenous_land) * (1 -( forest_protection_policy_effectiveness)) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_abandonment_rate = Pasture_Area*PASTURE_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_expansion_rate = TOTAL_TIMBER_DEMAND*TIMBER_EXPANSION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: This rate indicates how quickly the dedicated 'Legal Timber Extraction Areas' are expanding each year. It's driven by the overall timber demand and represents the growth of land specifically managed for legal timber harvesting.
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.conversion_to_pasture_area = pasture_expansion_demand_rate*PASTURE_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY*(DELAY((Cleared_Land_Area); 2)) {UNIFLOW}
    OUTFLOW PRIORITY: 1
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Cleared land area available for pasture conversion after a delay period.
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.conversion_to_legal_timber_extraction = legal_timber_expansion_rate*TIMBER_CONVERSION_EFFICIENCY*(Cleared_Land_Area/100) {UNIFLOW}
    OUTFLOW PRIORITY: 2
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.legal_timber_extraction_abandonment_rate = Legal_Timber_Extraction_Area*LEGAL_TIMBER_ABANDONMENT_FACTOR {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.newly_cleared_land = total_deforestation_rate+pasture_abandonment_rate+legal_timber_extraction_abandonment_rate {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: All deforested land first becomes 'Cleared_land' before conversion
: c Overall_strategy_cost = ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Increase_market_accessibility*Market_access_cost)+(land_right_cost*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Women_engagement_initiatives*Women_Engagement_cost)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Education_and_knowledge_transfer*Education_cost)+("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Training_and_capacity_building*Training_costs)+(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation*Coordination_costs)+(Engagement_cost*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Engagement)+(Forest_restoration_cost*LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Forest_conservation_policy)+(Monitoring_cost*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Enhance_environmental_monitoring)
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.deforestation_impact_on_environmental_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate * DEFORESTATION_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.pasture_expansion_impact_on_environmental_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.pasture_expansion_demand_rate*PASTURE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.fire_impact_on_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.fire_induced_deforestation_rate*FIRE_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.illegal_activities_impact_on_environmental_degradation = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land) * ILLEGAL_ACTIVITIES_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Combined impact of all illegal activities (both indigenous and non-indigenous areas) on environmental degradation. The impact of illegal activities on the environment is not only a function of the area converted/deforested, but also of the way in which the activity is conducted, and this method is inherently more destructive when the activity is illegal and unregulated.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.conservation_impact_on_degradation = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES+INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.degradation_rate = (deforestation_impact_on_environmental_degradation + pasture_expansion_impact_on_environmental_degradation + fire_impact_on_degradation + illegal_activities_impact_on_environmental_degradation) * (1 - Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION)* (1 + (1 - Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) * SOIL_DEGRADATION_AMPLIFIER)-conservation_impact_on_degradation {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Total rate of environmental degradation, influenced by various human activities. The (1 - ...) term ensures it slows down as degradation approaches its maximum.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.environmental_policy_effectiveness = Base_policy_effectiveness*(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity+INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness)
    UNITS: Dimensionless
    DOCUMENT: Overall effectiveness of environmental policies (0=none, 1=perfect). Higher values enhance recovery.
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.environmental_recovery_rate = BASE_ENVIRONMENTAL_RECOVERY_RATE * (1 + environmental_policy_effectiveness) * (Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of environmental recovery, enhanced by policy effectiveness and faster when degradation is high.
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.soil_recovery_rate = BASE_SOIL_RECOVERY_RATE * (1 - Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) * (1 + forest_area_impact_on_soil_recovery)* (1 - (Environmental_Degradation / MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) * ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION_IMPACT_ON_SOIL_RECOVERY) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of soil quality recovery. It slows down as soil quality approaches its maximum, and is enhanced by larger forest areas.
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.pasture_impact_on_soil_quality = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Pasture_Area*PASTURE_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.deforestation_impact_on_soil_quality = LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.total_deforestation_rate*DEFORESTATION_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.illegal_activities_impact_on_soil_quality = (LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.land_grabbing_pressure_on_non_indigenous_forest+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_pasture_pressure_on_indigenous_land+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_deforestation_rate_non_indigenous+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.illegal_logging_pressure_on_indigenous_land)*ILLEGAL_SOIL_DEGRADATION_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.soil_degradation_rate = (pasture_impact_on_soil_quality + deforestation_impact_on_soil_quality+illegal_activities_impact_on_soil_quality) * (Soil_Quality / MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Rate of soil quality degradation due to human activities. It slows down as soil quality approaches zero.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."indigenous_community_well-being_impact_on_engagement" = "Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"*"WELL-BEING_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR"
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Higher well-being fosters greater community engagement
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".institutional_capacity_for_engagement = INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".policy_engagement_initiatives_impact = institutional_capacity_for_engagement+LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Engagement_initiatives = Engagement*100
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".increasing_engagement = ("indigenous_community_well-being_impact_on_engagement" + policy_engagement_initiatives_impact+Engagement_initiatives) * (1 - Indigenous_Community_Engagement / MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".people_trust_in_institutions_decline = (1 - INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.People_Trust_in_Institutions / INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_PEOPLE_TRUST) * PEOPLE_TRUST_DECLINE_FACTOR
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".trust_decline_impact_on_egagement = people_trust_in_institutions_decline*TRUST_DECLINE_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_contribution =  CULTURAL_EROSION_BASE_RATE   * MAX(0; (1 - "Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"/"MAX_WELL-BEING"))   * (1 - 0,2 * EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES      )
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_impact_on_indigenous_engagement = CULTURAL_EROSION_ENGAGEMENT_FACTOR*cultural_erosion_contribution
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".decreasing_engagement = ((trust_decline_impact_on_egagement+cultural_erosion_impact_on_indigenous_engagement)*Indigenous_Community_Engagement/MAX_COMMUNITY_ENGAGEMENT) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".access_to_market = BASE_ACCESS_TO_MARKET
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".financial_support_handicraft = BASE_FINANCIAL_SUPPORT
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".community_support_handicraft = (Indigenous_Community_Engagement+2*Women_Engagement+2*Indigenous_Knowledge)*COMMUNITY_SUPPORT_FACTOR
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".empowerment_impact_on_creation = FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_creation = (availability_of_raw_material_for_handicraft * access_to_market * financial_support_handicraft * community_support_handicraft) * (1 - Handicraft_Activities / MAX_HANDICRAFT_ACTIVITIES) * (1 + MARKET_ACCESS_FACTOR) + empowerment_impact_on_creation + AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS+EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES+(INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation/2) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".MARKET_ACCESS_IMPACT_ON_COMPETITION = IF TIME > 2030 THEN Increase_market_accessibility ELSE 0
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_closure = Handicraft_Activities * COMPETITION_PRESSURE_HANDICRAFT * (1 - MARKET_ACCESS_IMPACT_ON_COMPETITION) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".handicraft_activities_contribution_to_knowledge = Handicraft_Activities * (Handicraft_Activities / MAX_HANDICRAFT_ACTIVITIES)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".engagement_contribution_to_knowledge = (Indigenous_Community_Engagement+Women_Engagement)*ENGAGEMENT_KNOWLEDGE_FACTOR+4*COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".knowledge_gain_rate =   (4*handicraft_activities_contribution_to_knowledge + engagement_contribution_to_knowledge) * (1 - Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".knowledge_loss_rate = ((cultural_erosion_contribution)*Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."handicraft_contribution_to_well-being" = (Handicraft_Activities * "HANDICRAFT_WELL-BEING_FACTOR")
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."environmental_quality_contribution_to_well-being" = (1-ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION)*"ENVIRONMENTAL_WELL-BEING_FACTOR"*(ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality/ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_SOIL_QUALITY)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Contribution of environmental quality (low degradation, high soil quality) to indigenous well-being.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."indigenous_knowledge_contribution_to_well-being" = Indigenous_Knowledge*"KNOWLEDGE_WELL-BEING_FACTOR"
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."well-being_increase" = ("handicraft_contribution_to_well-being"+"environmental_quality_contribution_to_well-being"+"indigenous_knowledge_contribution_to_well-being"+0,9*INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Policy_coordination_and_cooperation)*(1-"Indigenous_Community_Well-Being"/"MAX_WELL-BEING") {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Factors contributing to the increase in indigenous well-being. Slows down as max well-being is approached.
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".resources_scarcity_impact = ( (ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Environmental_Degradation / ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION) + (1 - ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.Soil_Quality / ENVIRONMENTAL_DEGRADATION.MAX_SOIL_QUALITY) ) / 2 * RESOURCE_SCARCITY_IMPACT_FACTOR
    UNITS: 1/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".social_disruption_impact = ( (cultural_erosion_contribution / CULTURAL_EROSION_BASE_RATE) * SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_AMPLIFIER * BASE_SOCIAL_DISRUPTION_IMPACT_RATE)/(Women_Engagement/100)
    UNITS: 1/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING"."well-being_decrease" = (resources_scarcity_impact+social_disruption_impact)*"Indigenous_Community_Well-Being" {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_access_to_resources = BASE_WOMEN_ACCESS_TO_RESOURCES * (1 + Handicraft_Activities * HANDICRAFT_IMPACT_ON_WOMEN_RESOURCES) + FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".institutional_capacity_for_women_initiatives = INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.Institutional_Capacity/INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_initiatives_impact = (BASE_WOMEN_INITATIVES*institutional_capacity_for_women_initiatives)+Women_engagement_initiatives
    UNITS: Dimensionless/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_increase_rate = (women_access_to_resources+women_engagement_initiatives_impact)*(1-Women_Engagement/MAX_WOMEN_ENGAGEMENT) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_barriers_to_engagement = BASE_CULTURAL_BARRIERS*(1-Indigenous_Knowledge/MAX_INDIGENOUS_KNOWLEDGE)
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Traditional knowledge may reduce barriers
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".cultural_erosion_impact_on_women_engagement = cultural_erosion_contribution*CULTURAL_EROSION_WOMEN_FACTOR
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".women_engagement_reduction_rate = ((cultural_barriers_to_engagement+cultural_erosion_impact_on_women_engagement)*Women_Engagement/MAX_WOMEN_ENGAGEMENT) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Social_disruption_barrier = social_disruption_impact*100
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.information_sharing_effectiveness = IF Institutional_Capacity < 40 THEN 10 ELSE IF Institutional_Capacity < 80 THEN 70 ELSE 100
    UNITS: Percentage
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.information_sharing_with_the_community = BASE_INFORMATION_SHARING   + (Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness * information_sharing_effectiveness)   + ("INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".Indigenous_Community_Engagement * 0,03)   + 2 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES   + 3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS
    UNITS: Percentage
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.increasing_awareness =   EDUCATION_CAMPAIGNS_EFFECTIVENESS * information_sharing_with_the_community   * (1 - Deforestation_Awareness / MAX_DEFORESTATION_AWARENESS)   + 0,2 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".EDUCATION_PROGRAMMES   + 0,3 * "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".AWARENESS_CAMPAIGNS {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.decreasing_awareness = Deforestation_Awareness*AWARENESS_DECAY_RATE {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.TRAINING_INVESTMENTS = Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
    DOCUMENT: Level of investments in institutional personal training
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.training_investments_effective = TRAINING_INVESTMENTS+1*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION = BASE_INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION+1*"INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION+Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.INVESTMENTS_IN_INSTITUTIONAL_COOPERATION = Policy_coordination_and_cooperation
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.people_trust_in_institutions_impact_on_capacity = People_Trust_in_Institutions*TRUST_CAPACITY_FACTOR+TRACEABILITY_SYSTEMS
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.increasing_capacity =   ( training_investments_effective * TRAINING_INVESTMENT_EFFECTIVENESS * (0,5 + 0,3*MIN(1; "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT                   + "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION))   + INSTITUTIONS_LEVEL_OF_COOPERATION * INVESTMENTS_IN_INSTITUTIONAL_COOPERATION * (0,5 + 0,3*MIN(1; "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".FINANCING_TRAINING_IMPACT                   + "INDIGENOUS_WELL-BEING".COOPERATIVES_PROMOTION))   + people_trust_in_institutions_impact_on_capacity * (0,5 + 0,2*public_awareness) )   * (1 - Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY)   + 0,2 * LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.FOREST_CONSERVATION_AND_RESTORATION_PROGRAMMES   + 0,3 * LANDUSE_CONFLICTS.Secure_indigenous_land_right {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.decreasing_capacity = (INSTITUTIONAL_INSTABILITY * CORRUPTION_LEVEL*2) * Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.ENVIRONMENTAL_MONITORING_FUNDING = Enhance_environmental_monitoring
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.institutional_capacity_impact_on_monitoring = Institutional_Capacity/MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: c INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.EFFECTIVENESS_BUILD_RATE = Enhance_environmental_monitoring
    UNITS: Dimensionless
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.monitoring_increase = (ENVIRONMENTAL_MONITORING_FUNDING/ REQUIRED_MONITORING_FUNDING) * institutional_capacity_impact_on_monitoring * EFFECTIVENESS_BUILD_RATE * 50*(1 - Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness / MAX_MONITORING_EFFECTIVENESS) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
: f INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY.monitoring_decrease = Environmental_Monitoring_Effectiveness * BASE_DECAY_RATE_MONITORING *(1+ (1 - Institutional_Capacity / MAX_INSTITUTIONAL_CAPACITY)*0,5) {UNIFLOW}
    UNITS: Percentage/Year
